{"tid":603000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"轉載自香討     [健身中心]\t    P記健身教練","createTime":"2018-03-23T10:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T11:12:55.000Z","uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33d52e4af92792caa7e3ebc3d57ddd8712ca540b","tid":603000,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27328674&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27328674%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=UMigsLiDAYQDA6SGr28idkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=31d6b57d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27328674&amp;extra=page%3D1</a><br />\n原文網址<br />\n<br />\n奉勸各位千萬唔好報physxxx嘅教練，佢地又hea又狗。本人新手玩健身，入會之餘都報左教練堂，$800一堂，頭3堂個教練都認真教，第四堂就要求買多啲堂，我唔加堂佢就堂堂換教練練俾我hea操，之後仲換左另一個人跟我嘅堂。新果個頭兩堂又重新操啲基本野，又系話我點點點唔得，唔夠力冇咩肌肉之類，又系問我有咩計劃、玩幾耐，都系叫我要買夠一年。講左唔買之後就次次去都是但搵一個教訓俾我。佢老母最初叫我買堂果陣就講到會帶住我操，會度身訂造啲訓練方法、飲食餐單，會自己跟曬我啲weight training 同 stretch，而家話去上堂仲要我就番佢地時間先可以去上，俾咁L貴一堂仲要受呢班賤人氣，physxxx真系好野！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要800蚊堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0c92eb5275e8b74cad228a8272b0f0f3a9bc6d","tid":603000,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"搵P記啲教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重衰過小學體育老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /